**Key design decisions:**
- Dark theme is the default (per task spec), toggled via `.dark` / `.light` on `<html>`
- Body tab is active on load with 3 sub-tabs: Overview (stat cards + metric rows), Body Map (placeholder), Trends (time-range pills + chart placeholder)
- Disabled tabs use `opacity: 0.45; pointer-events: none` on sidebar nav items and `opacity: 0.4` on mobile tabs, with "Coming Soon" overlay in content panels
- No Tailwind dependency — all utility classes defined directly in `app.css` following Blue2Scale naming conventions
- Public API exposed at `window.HealthAgent` for future data-binding code
